INSERT INTO
    fiskeridir_vessels (
    fiskeridir_vessel_id,call_sign,registration_id,name,length,building_year,engine_power,engine_building_year,fiskeridir_vessel_type_id,norwegian_municipality_id,norwegian_county_id,fiskeridir_nation_group_id,nation_id,gross_tonnage_1969,gross_tonnage_other,rebuilding_year
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::BIGINT[],$2::TEXT[],$3::TEXT[],$4::TEXT[],$5::DECIMAL[],$6::INT[],$7::INT[],$8::INT[],$9::INT[],$10::INT[],$11::INT[],$12::TEXT[],$13::TEXT[],$14::INT[],$15::INT[],$16::INT[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (fiskeridir_vessel_id) DO NOTHING
